data.description: This home is just amazing with all the features one could just about want. As you drive up you notice the corner lot and all of the parking space that comes with this property. As you enter this home you will notice the original fully restored hardwood floors split bedroom style living Tile in both the bathrooms and the kitchen. The spacious master suite set off to itself with a large walk-in closet. Step outside to covered patios and a large workshop 30x56 w 15' side walls 2 walk-thru doors 14'x16' wide drive in door Separate 200amp power Concrete in-ground storm shelter RV hook up w water sewer & power Come on out to see this beautiful home today all the features are here. All info to be verified by the buyer
